January 11, 2018 / 7:10 PM / Updated 27 minutes ago BRIEF-Aetna Says California Department Of Health Care Services Approves Aetna's Participation In Medi-Cal Reuters Staff 1 Min Read 
Jan 11 (Reuters) - Aetna Inc: 
* AETNA INC - CALIFORNIA DEPARTMENT OF HEALTH CARE SERVICES HAS APPROVED AETNA‘S PARTICIPATION IN MEDI-CAL, STATE‘S MEDICAID MANAGED CARE PROGRAM Source text for Eikon: Further company coverage:
